02:03:15,447 --> 02:03:20,942
- Here's a hundred bucks to start.
- Can't I get a job instead?

996
02:03:21,019 --> 02:03:25,956
A job?
What the hell can you do?

997
02:03:26,024 --> 02:03:27,855
I can clean.

998
02:03:29,227 --> 02:03:31,695
I ain't got no work
for a 12-year-old kid...

999
02:03:31,763 --> 02:03:33,856
so get it out
of your goddamn head!

1000
02:03:33,932 --> 02:03:36,662
It's over!
The game's over!

1001
02:03:36,735 --> 02:03:39,465
Leon's dead!

1002
02:03:39,538 --> 02:03:41,506
You hear me?

1003
02:03:48,713 --> 02:03:53,446
Come on. You think
I ain't hurtin' too?

1004
02:03:58,924 --> 02:04:01,324
But he's dead.

1005
02:04:01,393 --> 02:04:05,352
You're gonna forget all this craziness
and get your little ass back to school.

1006
02:04:06,598 --> 02:04:09,692
Now take this money
and get the hell outta here.

1007
02:04:09,768 --> 02:04:11,861
Don't let me see your face
till next month...

1008
02:04:11,937 --> 02:04:16,203
'cause something tells me
I'm about to lose my famous kind streak.

1009
02:05:07,459 --> 02:05:10,917
My parents...

1010
02:05:10,996 --> 02:05:13,089
died...

1011
02:05:13,164 --> 02:05:17,760
in a car accident
four weeks ago.

1012
02:05:17,836 --> 02:05:19,770
It was terrible.

1013
02:05:22,340 --> 02:05:26,106
We didn't have the time to get to know
one another when you first came here...

1014
02:05:26,177 --> 02:05:30,910
but I want you to know I'm not the kind
of woman who'd let down a child...

1015
02:05:30,982 --> 02:05:34,315
whatever her situation,
whatever her mistake.

1016
02:05:34,386 --> 02:05:39,449
So I'm going to help you and do my best
to welcome you here again.

1017
02:05:41,359 --> 02:05:44,021
But on one condition:

1018
02:05:44,095 --> 02:05:47,292
You have to stop lying to me,
Mathilda.

1019
02:05:47,365 --> 02:05:49,526
I want you to take a chance...

1020
02:05:49,601 --> 02:05:52,536
and trust me.

1021
02:05:52,604 --> 02:05:55,129
Tell me what happened to you.

1022
02:05:58,543 --> 02:06:01,637
My family got shot down
by D.E.A. officers...

1023
02:06:01,713 --> 02:06:05,149
because of a drug problem.

1024
02:06:05,216 --> 02:06:07,810
I left with the greatest guy on Earth.

1025
02:06:07,886 --> 02:06:12,653
He was a hit man, the best in town,
but he died this morning.

1026
02:06:12,724 --> 02:06:16,592
If you don't help me,
I'll be dead by tonight.

1027
02:06:35,981 --> 02:06:39,644
- You know her?
- I've never seen her.

1028
02:07:06,211 --> 02:07:08,873
I think we'll be okay here.
